{"content": "I need to multiply 242 \u00d7 808 in base 11.\n\n**Step 1: Convert 242 (base 11) to base 10**\n- 242\u2081\u2081 = 2\u00d711\u00b2 + 4\u00d711\u00b9 + 2\u00d711\u2070\n- = 2\u00d7121 + 4\u00d711 + 2\u00d71\n- = 242 + 44 + 2\n- = 288\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Convert 808 (base 11) to base 10**\n- 808\u2081\u2081 = 8\u00d711\u00b2 + 0\u00d711\u00b9 + 8\u00d711\u2070\n- = 8\u00d7121 + 0 + 8\u00d71\n- = 968 + 0 + 8\n- = 976\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Multiply in base 10**\n- 288 \u00d7 976 = 281,088\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 4: Convert 281,088 back to base 11**\n- 281,088 \u00f7 11 = 25,553 R 5\n- 25,553 \u00f7 11 = 2,323 R 0\n- 2,323 \u00f7 11 = 211 R 2\n- 211 \u00f7 11 = 19 R 2\n- 19 \u00f7 11 = 1 R 8\n- 1 \u00f7 11 = 0 R 1\n\nReading remainders from bottom to top: 182205\n\n**Answer: 182205**", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 363, "completion_tokens": 394}